Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Private Equity
Ridgemont Partners Management, LLC operates as a private equity firm. The Company invests in energy, healthcare, telecommunication, media, and technology sectors. Ridgemont Partners Management serves customers in the States of North Carolina and Texas.




