About the Firm
The name Ridgemont is inspired by the nearby Blue Ridge Mountains, a span of ridges that is a foundation of strength and longevity.  The Ridgemont team offers over two decades of private equity experience, bringing a broad perspective and partnership based approach to building middle market leaders.

MEET THE TEAM









